snippet.title: The Sandwich Making Experience - Pre Release Trailer
snippet.description: The Sandwich Making Experience is an asymmetrical party game that is designed to bring instant entertainment to any gathering. In The Sandwich Making Experience, players take turn being the sandwich maker, and the sandwich breaker, both competing to complete their objectives.
